"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"#### Sovryn is:\\n\\n* A non-custodial and permission-less smart contract-based system for bitcoin lending, borrowing, and margin trading.\\n* The RSK, Bitcoin side-chain built DAO built that provides Bitcoin with superpowers.\\n* The most feature-rich DeFi platform for Bitcoin.\\n\\n#### Currently Available Features\\n\\n* Spot-Exchange – a low-cost, low-slippage, AMM allowing instant trades between tokens.\\n* Perpetual Swaps – BTC-backed perpetual swaps allowing trades.\\n* Portfolio management and RSK (BTC) – Ethereum – BSC token bridge.\\n* Margin Trading – Creates up to 5X long/short trades, allowing users to borrow leverage from the lending pool.\\n* Lending Pool – Allows HODLers to earn interest by lending tokens to margin traders and borrowers.\\n  * Yield Farming\\n* Borrow – Allows users and smart contracts to borrow tokens from the lending pool. All lending is over-collateralized.\\n* SOV staking for platform rewards and airdrops.\\n* FastBTC Relay – Allows the use of Bitcoin almost instantly with smart contracts and decentralized products from any Bitcoin wallet.\\n* Bitcoin-backed stablecoin – users can use a USD-pegged token backed by overcollateralized bitcoin.\\n* Token sales on the Origin platform\\n  * Launchpad\\n* Bitocracy – An incentive-aligned protocol governance. Every future movement is openly discussed on Sovryn’s social channels, then moved to the official Bitocracy forum, then moved to the Sovryn dApp governance reconciliation, where each staker has the right to vote for an aim of the future platform development.\",\"timestamp\":1638432992,\"title\":\"DeFi on Bitcoin with SOVRYN\"},\"digest\":\"R_VwJzpNqHNovYBCnfZ3zSL6nmqbTgO882HbMitNzbU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x96FCE4b071C6d01Ea36551615fc2ccBF98b00ceD\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0_55V1CiCiJE8VTaUyJJ5QotZFGHFT-kexTfjv3j0hs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HttZMmCP4KBcufh63j2WxgWMqlE6aHhqLJT8-WUr704\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Wduxi-MbQd3Bb_37WY0cOoGTXTL_cOffbmuuFiqj7Q1ONhSstXnJNkMv6673jJ2DoJgUaIeM9d5wgS5KRE78tQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xecc380b491d26fa490a2214f01c99ca093e775087d26d5bb02815211c8b05fca50f238f2566b29decc77f0004fbd75d4144a7ac6e648e5cf340364ce31dd25a61b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0_55V1CiCiJE8VTaUyJJ5QotZFGHFT-kexTfjv3j0hs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HttZMmCP4KBcufh63j2WxgWMqlE6aHhqLJT8-WUr704\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"R_VwJzpNqHNovYBCnfZ3zSL6nmqbTgO882HbMitNzbU\"}"